data.description: NEW LOWER PRICE!!!  You must see this unique property just minutes away from the interstate and Croom yet still in the country.  You get 2 homes on one lot.  The first home is a 2/1 with a porch.  The second home is a 1/1, just perfect for an in-law suite or as a rental at the end of a paved road.  The huge Mulberry tree blooms every year, Muscadine grape vines, and a huge greenhouse with raised beds that is already set up with a watering system for those that love gardening.  There a huge shed with plenty of room for tools and storage.  One end of the shed has a bar set up with a sink, refrigerator, and a small bathroom.  This property has so much to offer at a great price.  Enough room to add your own pool.  Come make this your home for the best in country living.  SELLER VERY MOTIVATED. All reasonable offers considered. Possible additional 1/4 acre can be added to sale.
